ations wnctfm was concurrently divested to inner banks media to comply with fcc ownership limits the sale was completed on may   stations by stateedit delaware wjbrfm florida whfs whsr wjbx wjpt wlld wpbb wqykfm wrbqfm wrxkfm wsbr wwcn wwnn wxkb wyuu georgia waec wchzfm wdrr wgac wgacfm wgusfm whhd wkxcfm wrdw wwwe massachusetts wbos wbqt wklbfm wmjx wrca wrorfm michigan wcsx wmgcfm wrif new jersey wctc wdhafm wjrzfm wmgq wmtr wrat wtmr nevada kcye kdwn kklz koas kvgs north carolina wazz wbavfm wbcn wflb wkml wkqc wnks wpeg wsocfm wuks wzfx pennsylvania wbenfm wmgk wmmr wpen wtel wwdb referencesedit  a b fiscal year  consolidated net revenue retrieved    a b c d bbgi at a glance forbes magazine website retrieved   a b beasley announces beasley media group all access january   retrieved june     a b beasley announces beasley media group inc pdf press release january   retrieved june     company profile for beasley broadcast group inc bbgi retrieved    about retrieved june     cbs and beasley swap philadelphiamiami for charlottetampa from radio insight october    venta lance december   cbs beasley deal closes radioinsight retrieved december     beasley closes on greater media purchase makes multiple staff moves  beasley purchasing greater media for  million july   retrieved july     layden laura february   beasley to sell six stations in north carolina for  million naples daily news retrieved june     consummation notice wsflfm etc cdbs public access federal communications commission may   retrieved june     consummation notice wnctfm cdbs public access federal communications commission may   retrieved june    external linksedit beasley broadcast group website yahoo  beasley broadcasting group profile v t e beasley broadcast group radio stations delaware wjbrfm florida whfs whsr wjbx wjpt wlld wpbb wqykfm wrbqfm wrxkfm wsbr wwcn wwnn wxkb wyuu georgia waec wchzfm wdrr wgac wgacfm wgusfm whhd wkxcfm wrdw wwwe massachusetts wbos wbqt wklbfm wmjx wrca wrorfm michigan wcs